value.0: A large, solid piece of granite juts out from the ground. A small stone is embedded in the rock, it has a faint aura to it, and perhaps may be hammered out from the desert stone.

This roughly-polished stone is incised with a few runes spelling out prayers to Grumbar. When used, it will summon an earth elemental to the service of the user. It is of unusual hardness and could perhaps be forged into the most exotic of items by a skilled stonesmith.
This is an oddly-shaped bit of roughly polished rock, incised with a few runes.
High Stone of Controlling Earth Elementals
